Package games

Class Game

  • java.lang.Object
    • games.Game
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    MatrixGame

    public abstract class Game
extends java.lang.Object
    This is a (slightly) modified version of the gamut Game class. Main difference is that it does not inherit the parameterizations stuff.
